{"tid":179691,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一件中學時期朋友對你做過仆街嘅事","createTime":"2017-03-30T12:02:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-07T04:58:10.000Z","uid":96098,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0e442de1810a757a12c8929bf9caa348f078c76c","tid":179691,"uid":96098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T12:02:34.000Z","msg":"我先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n記得有次中午放飯就同埋班朋友去麵鋪食麵，當啲食物到齊而人人享用緊嘅時候<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢將啲辣椒漿倒落我碗麵喥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔憤氣嘅我作出反擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 只不過喺倒些少辣椒油落佢碗麵喥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢即刻發老脾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同我哋講我唔食啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你哋分咗碗麵啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我心諗：喂大佬先撩者賤 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你唔整我 我唔整你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你整人就可以，人哋整返你就唔可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 玩唔起就唔好玩人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 互不侵犯就最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 結果佢到依加都唔覺得佢有錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcc40996159b8aee94bece704f7e6c4d27c50443","tid":179691,"uid":20460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T12:24:57.000Z","msg":"辣椒漿定辣椒醬呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cb818bdcec4698f88c9555d4ddb2af525067f69","tid":179691,"uid":96098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T12:26:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>辣椒漿定辣椒醬呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blo